{"product_id":"hej-sensitive-oil-serum-30ml","title":"HEJ Organic Sensitive Oil-Serum 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle oil with a light texture. I give your skin a silky feeling, surprisingly non-oily, but with the right amount of glow. After all, the focus should not be on me, but on your radiant complexion.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExtra portion of care counteracts tense skin and gives it a rich glow\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVery light texture without an oily feeling on the skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePower active ingredient complex made from hemp oil, oat and chamomile extract provides intensive moisture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSkin type: Especially for sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAllergen-reduced perfume oil, 100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eHemp Oil\u003c\/span\u003e contains important Omega-6 fatty acids, is cell-regenerating and protects the skin without overgreasing it.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOat Extract\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-inflammatory and calming effect and is particularly suitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eChamomile Extract\u003c\/span\u003e intensively moisturises, is extra gentle and has an antibacterial effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply it to your face in the morning and evening after cleansing (approx. 2-3 drops) or mix it into your day or night cream\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil, Coco-Caprylate, Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil*, Shea Butter Ethyl Esters, Brassica Campestris Sterols, Cetearyl Alcohol, Polyglyceryl-6 Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate, Tocopherol, Glycerin, Aqua, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract*, Avena Sativa Kernel Extract*, Hypericum Perforatum Extract*, Alcohol, alpha-Bisabolol, Perfume** * Ingredients from Certified organic agriculture, * * Natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49513931374919,"sku":null,"price":15.4,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-sensitive-oil-serum-30ml-764330.png?v=1739897242","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hej-sensitive-oil-serum-30ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}